  <name>Codevis</name>
  <summary>Large Codebase Analyzer</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Codevis is a Large Scale software visualizer, focused on C++ codebases. it
      can help you identify issues and smells in your codebase. It also has an
      extensive plugin interface and some preliminary scripting support.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Generate a Visualization from Pre-Existing code</li>
      <li>Generate architectural code from a visualization</li>
      <li>Plugin System that allows you to add missing features</li>
      <li>Architectural linters (not just code linters)</li>
      <li>DBus support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
